(124,'PF Chang\'s Style Crispy Chicken Lettuce Wraps Recipe','1 Iceberg lettuce,1 Chicken breasts - cut into 1 cm cubes,2 teaspoons Sunflower Oil,Salt - to taste,1 teaspoon Black pepper powder,2 teaspoons Garlic - finely chopped,1/4 cup Button mushrooms - finely chopped,1/4 cup Spring Onion 
