(144,'Indo Chinese Crispy Chicken Chilli Recipe','250 grams Chicken - cut into medium sized pieces,Sunflower Oil - as required,2 tablespoons Garlic - minced,1 tablespoon Ginger - minced,2 Green Chillies - slit,1 Onion - sliced,1 Green Bell Pepper 
